Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Legion of Anubis
Covert Skins.desc: A custom paint job featuring Egyptian gods Anubis and Ra, representing the balance between life and death, has been applied.
Covert Skins.lore: May he tip the scales in your favor

Covert Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Printstream
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a stark black and white design and finished with pearlescent highlights.

Classified Skins.name: Glock-18 | Vogue
Classified Skins.desc: A pair of eyes grace the slide of this custom painted, Pop art inspired Glock.
Classified Skins.lore: "Look at me while I'm shooting at you!"

Classified Skins.name: XM1014 | Entombed
Classified Skins.desc: Entombed for millennia, this recently unearthed XM-1014 has been custom painted with blue wraps and Egyptian accents.

Classified Skins.name: M4A4 | Tooth Fairy
Classified Skins.desc: A custom paint job depicting incisors, molars, and a chilling take on the Tooth Fairy has been applied.
Classified Skins.lore: No one said the teeth have to be yours…

Restricted Skins.name: MP5-SD | Kitbash
Restricted Skins.desc: 20 years of MP5 designs have contributed to this custom paint job, held together by duct tape, zip ties, and glue.
Restricted Skins.lore: If at first (and second and third) you don't succeed…

Restricted Skins.name: Galil AR | Connexion
Restricted Skins.desc: Phoenix faction logos have been spray painted over its white and red base.
Restricted Skins.lore: They're bringing in the big guns

Restricted Skins.name: MAG-7 | Monster Call
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a blue base and underwater creatures in the foreground.
Restricted Skins.lore: There's always a bigger, greener fish

Restricted Skins.name: MAC-10 | Allure
Restricted Skins.desc: A woman in teal, believed to be iso onna, stands before koi fish and crashing waves on this custom painted MAC-10.

Restricted Skins.name: Tec-9 | Brother
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a brown and gold camo pattern and a T-sided agent beneath the rear sight.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: PP-Bizon | Runic
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: This custom paint job features runes of unknown origin and a magazine that resembles a Gatling gun.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SSG 08 | Mainframe 001
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A high tech custom paint job of blues and purples has been applied.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P2000 | Gnarled
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A twisted, alien being stretches from the grip down the slide of this hand painted P2000.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: From the dark corners of the infinite void

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P250 | Cassette
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A custom paint job inspired by video cassette packaging from the 1990s has been applied.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: P90 | Freight
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Its custom paint job resembles a train car covered in graffiti.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Negev | Ultralight
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a gray digital camo pattern and teal arrows.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: SG 553 | Ol' Rusty
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Originally polished steel, moisture has changed this weapon's appearance. "Ol' Rusty" has been stamped above the trigger casing.
